    <h2 id="recipe1">Chocolate Muffins</h2>
    
    <ul>
        <li>Time: 35 minutes</li>
        <li>Serves: 12</li>
    </ul>
    
    <table>
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>Ingredients</th>
                <th>Quantity</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td>All-purpose flour</td>
                <td>2 cups</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Cocoa powder</td>
                <td>1/2 cup</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Sugar</td>
                <td>1 cup</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Eggs</td>
                <td>2 large</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Milk</td>
                <td>1 cup</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Butter, melted</td>
                <td>1/2 cup</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Baking powder</td>
                <td>2 tsp</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Salt</td>
                <td>1/2 tsp</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Chocolate chips (optional)</td>
                <td>1/2 cup</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
    
    <p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Preheat your oven to 180°C (350°F) and line a muffin tin with paper liners.</p>
    <p><strong>Step 2:</strong> In a large bowl, whisk together the flour, cocoa powder, sugar, baking powder, and salt.</p>
    <p><strong>Step 3:</strong> In another bowl, beat the eggs, then add milk and melted butter.</p>
    <p><strong>Step 4:</strong> Pour the wet ingredients into the dry ingredients and mix until just combined. Fold in chocolate chips if using.</p>
    <p><strong>Step 5:</strong> Spoon the batter into the muffin tin and bake for 20–25 minutes, or until a toothpick comes out clean.</p>
    
    <p><em>Source: <a href="https://www.allrecipes.com/recipe/6865/to-die-for-chocolate-muffins/">AllRecipes: Chocolate Muffins</a></em></p>
    

